# CE planning artifacts

Compound Engineering skills default to `docs/brainstorms/` and `docs/plans/`. **In this repo, override those defaults.**

## Write paths

| Artifact | Directory | Filename pattern |
|----------|-----------|------------------|
| Requirements | `brainstorms/` | `YYYY-MM-DD-<topic>-requirements.md` |
| Implementation plans | `plans/` | `YYYY-MM-DD-NNN-<type>-<name>-plan.md` |

Create `brainstorms/` or `plans/` at the repo root if missing. **Do not** add new planning markdown under `docs/` — `docs/` is for the Zensical site only (`index.md`, `getting-started.md`, `roadmap.md`, `design/`).

## Read and search

When resuming, deepening, or linking CE work, search **`brainstorms/`** and **`plans/`** at repo root, not `docs/brainstorms/` or `docs/plans/`.

## Cross-references

- Plan frontmatter `origin:` → `brainstorms/<file>-requirements.md` (repo-relative, no `docs/` prefix)
- Links in plans/requirements to strategy → `STRATEGY.md` at repo root
- User-facing docs site → `docs/roadmap.md` only

## Rationale

Zensical does not support `exclude_docs`; CE markdown under `docs/` triggers build warnings. See `zensical.toml` comment.
